headline: What are the top holdings of Cathie Wood's ARK Innovation ETF?
summary: Tesla (TSLA) dominates Cathie Wood's ARK Innovation ETF (ARKK) holdings, but what other names back up the fund? Yahoo Finance Markets and Data Editor Jared Blikre, who also hosts Yahoo Finance's Stocks in Translation podcast, examines the fund's top holdings during its peak, including Tesla, Teladoc Health (TDOC), Roku (ROKU), Block (XYZ), and Shopify (SHOP), as well as its most recent holdings like Coinbase Global (COIN), Roblox (RBLX), and Palantir Technologies (PLTR). Twice a week, Stocks In Translation cuts through the market mayhem, noisy numbers and hyperbole to give you the information you need to make the right trade for your portfolio. You can find more episodes here, or watch on your favorite streaming service. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Catalysts here.
